Texts.Eng: A nice lookin' bunch of feathers.
Avian temples often feature bundles of large feathers from colorful birds.
Texts.Por: Templos Avians geralmente apresentam pacotes de grandes penas de pássaros coloridos.

Texts.Eng: Floran likess big featherss.  Wantss to hunt the bird they came from.
Texts.Por: Floran gosta de penass grandes. Quer caçar o pássaro de onde vieram.

Texts.Eng: Gorgeous, vibrant feathers arranged like flowers
Texts.Por: Penas lindas e vibrantes dispostas como flores

Texts.Eng: I'd hate to meet the bird that dropped these massive feathers.
Texts.Por: Eu odiaria encontrar o pássaro que deixou cair estas penas maciças.

Texts.Eng: I've never seen a bird with feathers this large.
Texts.Por: Eu nunca vi um pássaro com penas tão grandes.

Texts.Eng: The bird that had these feathers must have been quite large.
These feathers are beautiful and elegant.
Texts.Por: Estas penas são bonitas e elegantes.
